      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Appropriates funds to the Hawaii Technology Development Corporation to assist small businesses, including those related to the tourism sector, with technology enablement, including the adoption of artificial intelligence and advanced digital tools.  Requires the Hawaii Technology Development Corporation to submit a report to the Legislature."
